      "comment": "SPOT CHECK (7) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at this track over 300m behind Scelzi (18.21) in a Novice race. Has ability and is a key runner. KING KOOPA (2) had to overcome a collision with another runner and could manage only a distant fifth (17.99) in a Novice race over 300m at this track. Has the ability and can atone with the right run. KOMBI ACKEE (4) is racing well without winning, recording four minors on end, the latest when checked in the run and finishing second in a Novice race at this track (17.77). Has the ability and looks a key chance. AVATAR OF FUN (5) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
